{"tid":731198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(立法禁刀?) 中國再傳發生隨機砍人  8歲男童死亡","createTime":"2018-07-06T04:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T15:18:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f91fd9183339ad276f44897eae269dfb293e80","tid":731198,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/0ef9e6bb6b8b8c8c08b23619355c6da9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F0ef9e6bb6b8b8c8c08b23619355c6da9.jpg&h=c3989d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國再傳隨機砍人事件。一名男子周四中午在湖南省邵陽市隆回縣桃洪鎮南松村持刀見人就砍，造成7人受傷，其中一名8歲男童當場死亡。嫌犯目前已被當地警方逮捕。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《中央社》援引湖南省公安廳網路安全保衛與技術偵察總隊官方微博周四晚通報，中午12時43分，羅姓嫌犯（男，40歲，隆回縣桃洪鎮文昌村人，有故意傷害前科）在南松村持刀砍傷7人，包括4名成年人、3名兒童，其中1名8歲男童當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n羅姓嫌犯隨後搶奪一輛三輪車逃離現場。隆回縣公安局獲報後展開圍追堵截，已迅速將他抓獲。<br />\n<br />\n當地網民指出，中午12時許在桃洪鎮南松合作社附近，一名疑似吸毒而神智不清的男子持刀見人就砍，毫無防備的數名民眾被砍傷，有一名婦女身上抱著一個小孩已經全身是血、奄奄一息。<br />\n<br />\n6月28日，上海街頭驚傳隨機砍人，兇嫌殺死兩名男童，事件震動全國，並引發上海市民大規模追悼。<br />\n<br />\n周四適逢兩名男童的&ldquo;頭七&rdquo;，湖南再傳隨機砍人，又造成一名男童死亡，使中國網民既憤怒又感嘆中國社會到底出了什麼問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180705-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E5%82%B3%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%A8%E6%A9%9F%E7%A0%8D%E4%BA%BA-8%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20180705-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A0%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA-8%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=b39e440f\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180705-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E5%82%B3%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%A8%E6%A9%9F%E7%A0%8D%E4%BA%BA-8%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n中酸部表示未掌握有關情況, 不評論個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8d4a505a9df7c30742703ea75212fbf791ff74","tid":731198,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8548a38c46d948a48baf0fabc0f8c2104ecb51b4","tid":731198,"uid":90704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"一早話禁<br />\n班刀權撚呢？<br />\nBin <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380911f43965b8cdca8975bd1cde7e55a84866e5","tid":731198,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"中國咁多億人口<br />\n幾個%係傻人都玩殘你"},{"pid":"1181bfae1be1f76b5389781f862a5178707fd325","tid":731198,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"380911f43965b8cdca8975bd1cde7e55a84866e5","tid":731198,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"中國咁多億人口<br />\n幾個%係傻人都玩殘你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"可能只有幾個%唔係儍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6fcad584e9aaf753a985c4aadd93fd91ec8157","tid":731198,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"係咪琴晚有fb片個個呀伯？"},{"pid":"bf4c1fb72c365c73618b034b8b7f7940827d7539","tid":731198,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6fcad584e9aaf753a985c4aadd93fd91ec8157","tid":731198,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"係咪琴晚有fb片個個呀伯？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2